
Overview of noun nirvana

The noun nirvana has 2 senses (first 1 from tagged texts)
                                        
1. (1) nirvana, enlightenment -- ((Hinduism and Buddhism) the beatitude that transcends the cycle of reincarnation; characterized by the extinction of desire and suffering and individual consciousness)
2. Eden, paradise, nirvana, heaven, promised land, Shangri-la -- (any place of complete bliss and delight and peace)
